data.description: Discover the best of living in family friendly Spartan Lake Estates in Chatham! This pristine 2-year-old ranch home offers the perfect blend of style, space, and convenience. Boasting 4 spacious bedrooms and 2.5 baths, it's designed for your family's ultimate comfort. Step into the heart of the home – the upgraded kitchen! With great finishes, stainless steel appliances, and ample counter space, it's a chef's dream come true. The open-concept layout flows seamlessly into the living area, making entertaining a breeze.  Need a dedicated workspace or playroom? You'll love the separate office/playroom that provides flexibility for your needs. The possibilities are endless! Don't forget the partially finished basement – the perfect canvas for your creative ideas!  Outside, the large backyard offers endless possibilities for outdoor fun and relaxation. Whether you're hosting a barbecue on the covered back porch or enjoying a quiet evening under the stars, this space is your private oasis. The 3 acre pond is a couple minute walk and provides awesome wildlife and is fully stocked with fun fish to catch and eat, including walleye!  Make this nearly new construction home in Spartan Lake Estates, yours and experience convenience of a finished yard and landscaping that new homes often don't have. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity – schedule your showing today!
